short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Easily transfer answers between forms for an improved experience. Supports Google Forms, MyAloha. Simple, efficient, and productive.

long.ar,de,es,fr,hi,id,ja,ko,pl,ru,th,zh_CN,z:
Effortlessly copy answers from completed Google Forms and paste them into another form with just a few clicks. Easily extract responses in a clean, readable format or a compact text-code, perfect for sharing or personal use.

Save time, stay organized, and collaborate smoothly with this great tool for form and exam answer management!

v4.1.0:
MyAloha Compatibility: Partial support for MyAloha exams allows you to copy answers from in-progress exams to share with friends or use shared codes from others to paste answers directly into your MyAloha exam

v.4.2.0:
- Improved performance and optimized code for a lighter footprint
- Enhanced error handling for better reliability
- Minor UI updates for an improved user experience

v.4.3.0 Update:
- Multi-language Support: Now includes English and Vietnamese language options, enhancing accessibility for a broader user base. Additional languages such as Indonesian, Chinese, French, and German will be added in the next update.
- Questions and answers are automatically pasted when the share button is clicked, making the sharing process faster and more efficient.
